at|^b^*bAns^*n
It is likely that LHO holds the Ace of diamonds.  It is important to take three diamond tricks.  If you win trick one and then lose to LHO's Queen of diamonds, RHO will be able to lead a heart.  The Queen will be covered by the King and whether you win or duck, your Ace will be forced while the Ace of diamonds is still out.
The key here to hold off until hearts have been played again.
That way, you will be sure to set up three diamond tricks since RHO will not be able to lead a heart after taking the Queen of diamonds.
